best breakup album ever just a short commentary - written after a painful divorce , `` bare '' is a haunting summary of the many emotions that come crashing in following a breakup . musically , the songs have all the pop expertise you 'd expect from al - combined with lyrics that lay bare the pain and hope of starting over again . buy it . buy it for your friends who 've been left behind by a lover or a husband , buy it for yourself . i keep it in my album rotation for sad days